name: Star Rating
description:
🤔 What's this?

This is a star template commonly used for scoring ratings ⭐️ 🌟 ✨.


🤔 How to use it?

  • Copy star and stars into your project.
  • Adjust the width and height of the stars in the three states(Full, Half, None) of the variant at the same time.
  • Adjust the colour of the stars in different modes and the background colour.
  • Adjust the spacing of the stars.
